cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI

The paper focuses on human-robot interaction and the use of multiple modalities (speech, head movements, hand gestures) to disambiguate referring expressions. This suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of speech also suggests a potential focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and the use of computer vision to interpret hand gestures and head movements suggests a potential focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
